  "update_count": 98,
  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nThe Message Constructor[1] consider that the payload's size would always in Uint32 Range.However we can use (new WebAssembly.Memory({initial:65536})).buffer to get an ArrayBuffer which size is 0x100000000, larger than Uint32 Range.  \nThe payload's size would be truncated"
